ta-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这类任务最容易犯的错误，是把整份 PDF 原样交给模型。这样做看起来简单，但成本高、噪声大，而且图表和数字核查容易出错。正确做法是先做多模态拆解，把不同形态的数据转成最适合推理的表示。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f195f425  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="6008"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="6009"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="6009:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这套流程可以分三步。</span></span></span></div><h3 class="se-075e1886" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="6010"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="6011"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="6011:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">步骤一 融合层分发</span></span></span></h3><div class="se-55355f51  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="6012"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="6013"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="6013:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 接到 PDF 后，先由 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="6014" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="6015"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="6015:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">MultiModalFuser</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="6016"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="6016:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 拆分输入。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-25d6e71f" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="6017"><div class="se-11f9fb65 se-96b11d74"><span></span></div><div class="se-557745e6 se-8b14d2ad"><span></span></div><div class="se-6e814785"><div class="se-060dcc8f se-326def94" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-060dcc8f se-326def94" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-060dcc8f se-326def94" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-060dcc8f se-326def94" data-co